Pat Cullen (amụrụ n'afọ 1965) bụ onye nọọsụ Northern Irish na onye otu ọrụ
Kemgbe Julaị 2021, ọ bụ odeakwụkwọ ukwu nke Royal College of Nursing.
A mụrụ Cullen na Carrickmore, County Tyrone ma bụrụ nwa ikpeazụ n'ime ụmụ asaa.
Cullen rụrụ ọrụ dị ka onye nọọsụ obodo na ọdịda anyanwụ Belfast n'oge nsogbu ahụ

Ọ gara n'ihu na-arụ ọrụ na Public Health Agency na Health and Social Care Board, tupu ọ banye na Royal College of Nursing na 2016. Na Mee 2019, ọ ghọrọ onye nduzi nke Northern Ireland Board nke RCN. Ọ malitere ịrụ ọrụ dị ka odeakwụkwọ ukwu na onye isi nchịkwa n'ọnwa Eprel 2021, a họpụtakwara ya dị ka ode akwụkwọ ukwu na onye nduzi nke RCN mba na Julaị 2021.

Na ngwụcha afọ 2022, ọ duziri ọgbaghara nke National Health Service nke ndị nọọsụ Bekee na Welsh gbara ọsọ na nke mbụ ya n'akụkọ ihe mere eme nke afọ 106 nke ndị nọn. N'ọnwa Eprel 2023, ndị otu ya kwupụtara ọgbaghara na ngwụsị izu ezumike ụlọ akụ nke Mee (30 Eprel ruo 2 Mee) mgbe ndị otu RCN jụrụ onyinye ụgwọ ahụ.
